:false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Ioe+"}]},{"client_msg_id":"561bc5d6-6fc6-408a-87ac-72f54e9f213d","type":"message","user":"UJV04G927","text":"この人の設定が参考になるかもしれません。dein.vim使ってたと思います。\n\u003chttps://github.com/glepnir/nvim\u003e","ts":"1606877466.471300","attachments":[{"fallback":"GitHub: glepnir/nvim","id":1,"title":"glepnir/nvim","title_link":"https://github.com/glepnir/nvim","text":"neovim configuration written in lua. Contribute to glepnir/nvim development by creating an account on GitHub.","thumb_url":"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/41671631?s=400\u0026v=4","blocks":null,"service_name":"GitHub","service_icon":"https://a.slack-edge.com/80588/img/unfurl_icons/github.png","thumb_width":400,"thumb_height":400,"from_url":"https://github.com/glepnir/nvim","original_url":"https://github.com/glepnir/nvim"}],"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"PAWW"}]},{"client_msg_id":"7036b3d1-a48a-4b33-b355-62896bcd1520","type":"message","user":"U01D44KSY9Z","text":"完全にLuaへの理解度不足が敗因","ts":"1606877352.470300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"GWOut"}]},{"client_msg_id":"02e7f65d-cef3-431b-a437-1f5a0b740f98","type":"message","user":"U01D44KSY9Z","text":"Luaだと `vim.fn` の返り値をifで正確に判定してくれない事に今気付いた\n全部明示的に数字を判定するようにしたら上手く動きました","ts":"1606877194.470000","thread_ts":"1606877194.470000","reply_count":1,"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"hzG"}]},{"client_msg_id":"17dfc191-9611-4a7d-a25f-c74d0c091245","type":"message","user":"U01D44KSY9Z","text":"コードを書き換えてもよく分からなかったので、deinで使うruntimepathを変更したら動くようにはなりました\nただlazy指定のプラグインがなぜか重複して定義されてる扱いになっているようで、起動する度に警告が表示されてますが","ts":"1606876935.468500","thread_ts":"1606873172.466800","subtype":"thread_broadcast","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"hDMhd"}],"root":{"client_msg_id":"3d8ab1a5-53ce-48de-ba82-106da9d9f06e","type":"message","user":"U01D44KSY9Z","text":"`init.lua` を書いているんですが、そこでdeinを使ってプラグインを読み込ませたいんですよね\nとりあえず `init.vim` をそのままLuaに書き換えて\n```if vim.fn['dein#load_state'](dein_dir) then\n  vim.fn['dein#begin'](dein_dir)\n  local rc_dir = vim.fn.expand('~/.config/nvim')\n  local toml = rc_dir..'/dein.toml'\n  local lazy_toml = rc_dir..'/dein_lazy.toml'\n  vim.fn['dein#load_toml'](toml, { lazy = 0 })\n  vim.fn['dein#load_toml'](lazy_toml, {lazy = 1})\n  vim.fn['dein#end']()\n  vim.fn['dein#save_state']()\nend```\nとしたのはいいんですが、プラグイン側のVim Scriptが上手くパースできていないのか、プラグイン由来の関数が見つからない旨のエラーが複数出ているという状況です\nこれに関しては僕の書き方が悪いんだろうなとは思ってるんですが、どう書き換えたらいいかも分からず……","ts":"1606873172.466800","thread_ts":"1606873172.466800","edited":{"user":"U01D44KSY9Z","ts":"1606873182.000000"},"reply_count":1,"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"64hA"}]}},{"client_msg_id":"cec98224-e7f2-46ab-8809-d2384681c231","type":"message","user":"U7B4ZD49X","text":"お、プラグインマネージャーとの連携きた\n\u003chttps://github.com/nvim-telescope/telescope-packer.nvim\u003e","ts":"1606874656.468300","attachments":[{"fallback":"GitHub: nvim-telescope/telescope-packer.nvim","id":1,"title":"nvim-telescope/telescope-packer.nvim","title_link":"https://github.com/nvim-telescope/telescope-packer.nvim","text":"A Telescope extension that provides extra functionality for Packer.nvim - nvim-telescope/telescope-packer.nvim","thumb_url":"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/74419533?s=400\u0026v=4","blocks":null,"service_name":"GitHub","service_icon":"https://a.slack-edge.com/80588/img/unfurl_icons/github.png","thumb_width":400,"thumb_height":400,"from_url":"https://github.com/nvim-telescope/telescope-packer.nvim","original_url":"https://github.com/nvim-telescope/telescope-packer.nvim"}],"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"2unj"}